<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Automation on Mi&amp;Bee Blog</title><link>https://blog.mickeyzzc.tech/tags/automation/</link><description>Recent content in Automation on Mi&amp;Bee Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><managingEditor>蓝宝石的傻话</managingEditor><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 Feb 2017 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.mickeyzzc.tech/tags/automation/rss.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>SSL证书自动化管理——Ansible批量部署与更新实践</title><link>https://blog.mickeyzzc.tech/archives/11-ssl-auto/</link><pubDate>Mon, 13 Feb 2017 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.mickeyzzc.tech/archives/11-ssl-auto/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;SSL 证书管理是 IT 基础设施运维的一项常规工作。随着服务数量增长和证书更新周期缩短，手动管理证书效率低且容易出错。本文介绍如何用 Ansible 实现证书的批量部署与更新，以及配套的过期监控与自动续期方案。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>